<p class="ayah 22-6" id="6" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذَٲلِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">That</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِأَنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) because,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُوَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْحَقُّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) the Truth.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَنَّهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And that He</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُحْىِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[He] gives life</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمَوْتَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(to) the dead,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَنَّهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and that He</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) over</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُلِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">every</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَىْءٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">thing</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rt