" dir="rtl">فَجٍّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">mountain highway</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَمِيقٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">distant.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>27<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
