 second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) your Protector -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَنِعْمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">so an Excellent</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمَوْلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[the] Protector</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَنِعْمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and an Excellent</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلنَّصِيرُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[the] Helper.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>78<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
